Interface LandmarkOrdering

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LMOrdering

    public interface LandmarkOrdering
    LandmarkOrdering interface provides the necessary methods to work with orderings between landmark nodes in the landmarks graph (LG).

    1.0
